which was an insult.

00:51:25.480 --> 00:51:27.820
I should have given it back
to him, but I needed it,

00:51:27.820 --> 00:51:29.640
and I wanted to do a record.

00:51:29.640 --> 00:51:32.240
He said, I don't expect
you to sell by 500 records.

00:51:32.240 --> 00:51:33.450
I said, OK.

