00:51:41.704 --> 00:51:42.370
I have a new CD.

00:51:42.370 --> 00:51:44.350
It's called "A Few
Miles from Memphis."

00:51:44.350 --> 00:51:46.391
The first statement I got
from the record company

00:51:46.391 --> 00:51:48.520
was 3,500 copies.

00:51:48.520 --> 00:51:51.050
I said, uh-oh, you didn't
say I would sell but 500.

00:51:51.050 --> 00:51:52.700
But that was something
for me because I

00:51:52.700 --> 00:51:54.441
needed to get a product out.

00:51:54.441 --> 00:51:55.940
And it was a good
experience for me,

00:51:55.940 --> 00:51:59.237
but the thing I found out--
