to be as prepared as you can.

00:52:01.820 --> 00:52:04.890
When I went in, I made sure
all the notes were right,

00:52:04.890 --> 00:52:06.260
so we didn't lose a lot of time.

00:52:06.260 --> 00:52:09.220
Because when you're losing time,
changing notes, and doing this,

00:52:09.220 --> 00:52:11.260
that costs the record
company a lot of money.

00:52:11.260 --> 00:52:14.420
So that was my first venture
of doing something on my own.

00:52:14.420 --> 00:52:17.879
The record is called "A
Few Miles From Memphis."

