00:52:38.030 --> 00:52:39.110
is the city of jazz.

00:52:39.110 --> 00:52:41.250
Memphis is the
home of the blues.

00:52:41.250 --> 00:52:44.110
You see, blues, here's
the thing about the blues.

00:52:44.110 --> 00:52:47.280
Mr. Kurt Elling said something
